data.description: If you are looking for country living and privacy, this is the place.  Newly updated 3 bedroom 2 bath ranch on a full unfinished basement surrounded by 5 acres of woods and privacy.  Sit on your front porch with your coffee or cocktail and watch the deer and wildlife. Open living room, kitchen, and dining room.  Split bedroom plan puts you on one side and the kids on the other!! House has hardwood floors throughout with new carpet in the bedrooms.  Bathrooms have new vanities and light fixtures.  New deck with metal railings on back. All new stainless steel appliances remain.  Move in ready.  Lots of room for all of the toys in this beauty.
